#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattivagga "
msgstr "3. A Sword "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Mahaddhanasutta "
msgstr "28. Affluent "

#. HTML: </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.34, sc1
msgctxt "sn1.28:1.1"
msgid "“Mahaddhanā mahābhogā, "
msgstr "“The affluent and the wealthy, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:1.2"
msgid "raṭṭhavantopi khattiyā; "
msgstr "even the aristocrats who rule the land, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:1.3"
msgid "Aññamaññābhigijjhanti, "
msgstr "are jealous of each other, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:1.4"
msgid "kāmesu analaṅkatā. "
msgstr "insatiable in sensual pleasures. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn1.28:2.1"
msgid "Tesu ussukkajātesu, "
msgstr "Among those of such an avid nature, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:2.2"
msgid "bhavasotānusārisu; "
msgstr "flowing along the stream of lives, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Kedha taṇhaṃ → rodhataṇhaṃ (s1-3, km) | gedhataṇhaṃ (pts1-2, mr)
#. VAR: pajahiṃsu → pavāhiṃsu (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn1.28:2.3"
msgid "Kedha taṇhaṃ pajahiṃsu, "
msgstr "who here has given up craving? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:2.4"
msgid "ke lokasmiṃ anussukā”ti. "
msgstr "Who in the world is not avid?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.35, sc3
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.1"
msgid "“Hitvā agāraṃ pabbajitā, "
msgstr "“Having given up their home, their child, their cattle, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.2"
msgid "hitvā puttaṃ pasuṃ piyaṃ; "
msgstr "and all that they love, they went forth. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.3"
msgid "Hitvā rāgañca dosañca, "
msgstr "Having given up desire and hate, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.4"
msgid "avijjañca virājiya; "
msgstr "having dispelled ignorance, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.5"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā arahanto, "
msgstr "the perfected ones with defilements ended—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.28:3.6"
msgid "te lokasmiṃ anussukā”ti. "
msgstr "they in the world are not avid.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
